1a:["$","p","27",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Strengths: Speed (parallelism and caching), Docker-first, excellent test insights."]}]
1b:["$","p","28",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Weaknesses: Limited free tier, can get expensive at scale."]}]
1c:["$","h2","30",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"Containerization and Orchestration"}]
1d:["$","h3","32",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-8 mb-3","children":"Docker"}]
1e:["$","p","33",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Docker remains the standard for containerization. Docker Compose simplifies multi-container local development. Docker Desktop provides a GUI for container management."]}]
1f:["$","h3","35",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-8 mb-3","children":"Kubernetes"}]
20:["$","p","36",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Kubernetes (K8s) is the standard for container orchestration in production. Managed services like Amazon EKS, Google GKE, and Azure AKS reduce operational overhead. For smaller teams, tools like K3s offer lightweight alternatives."]}]
21:["$","h2","38",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"Infrastructure as Code"}]
22:["$","h3","40",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-8 mb-3","children":"Terraform (HashiCorp)"}]
23:["$","p","41",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Terraform is the leading IaC tool, supporting 2,000+ providers across AWS, Azure, GCP, and SaaS platforms. State management tracks infrastructure changes. HCL (HashiCorp Configuration Language) is declarative. Pricing: Free for up to 5 users, then $20/user/month."]}]
24:["$","h3","43",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-8 mb-3","children":"Ansible (Red Hat)"}]
25:["$","p","44",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Ansible is agentless configuration management and automation. It uses YAML-based playbooks and is ideal for configuration consistency. It excels at application deployment and multi-tier orchestration."]}]
26:["$","h2","46",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"Monitoring and Observability"}]
27:["$","h3","48",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-8 mb-3","children":"Datadog"}]
28:["$","p","49",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Datadog (rated 4.9/5 on our platform) unifies metrics, traces, and logs in a single platform. Its AI-powered alerts and dashboards provide real-time observability. Pricing: $15/host/month for infrastructure monitoring."]}]
29:["$","h3","51",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-8 mb-3","children":"Prometheus + Grafana"}]
2a:["$","p","52",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["The open-source monitoring stack. Prometheus collects metrics, Grafana visualizes them. Highly customizable but requires more setup than SaaS alternatives."]}]
2b:["$","h3","54",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-8 mb-3","children":"New Relic"}]
2c:["$","p","55",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["New Relic offers full-stack observability with APM, infrastructure monitoring, and log management. Its AI-driven anomaly detection surfaces issues proactively."]}]
2d:["$","h2","57",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"Building Your DevOps Stack"}]
2e:["$","p","59",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["A modern DevOps toolchain typically includes: GitHub (source control) + GitHub Actions (CI/CD) + Docker (containers) + Kubernetes (orchestration) + Terraform (infrastructure) + Datadog or Prometheus+Grafana (monitoring) + a secrets manager like HashiCorp Vault."]}]
2f:["$","h2","61",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"The ROI of Good DevOps"}]
30:["$","p","63",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Elite DevOps teams deploy on demand, have change failure rates under 5%, and recover from incidents in under an hour. They invest in automation early and treat their toolchain as a product that continuously improves. The upfront investment in DevOps tooling pays for itself within 3-6 months through reduced deployment friction and faster time-to-market."]}]
